### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts
Accept: application/json

### Get one post (example with id 1)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Post",
  "content": "This is a test post"
}

### Update a post (example with id 1)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post",
  "content": "Updated content"
}

### Delete a post (example with id 1)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/posts/1
